data.event: Culver spoke about this issue today at a meeting of the Dependent Care Task Force, where he was joined by Government Oversight Committee co-chairs Sen. Rich Olive, D-Story City and Rep. Vicki Lensing, D-Iowa City.

event.title: the past 30 years, bureaucracy at every level of government failed

data.event: “Over the past 30 years, bureaucracy at every level of government failed these men,” said Culver.
